Dialogue: 15,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I apologize for summoning you on such short notice.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}To be frank, I'd like to ask you for a favor.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes ma'am, how may I be of service?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to practice on you.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:14.81,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't used this on humans in quite some time.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 15,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set you free in just a minute.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 15,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:29.67,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 15,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You may rest at ease.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the coming of the Calm,
Dialogue: 15,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that the situation will change.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain of this?
Dialogue: 15,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:49.65,0:00:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I swear on my family's name, I will carry it out.
Dialogue: 15,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm is coming.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a stagnant time, when everything comes to a halt.
Dialogue: 15,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
