Dialogue: 15,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on! Please get up.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're going to be late.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:46.77,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Get out of bed already!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go get dressed!
Dialogue: 15,0:02:55.19,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I only transferred to this school so I'd have more opportunities to attack you, Mirai.
Dialogue: 15,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With that reason no longer valid, I see no need to—
Dialogue: 15,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Your uniform.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to talk.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Your hair is such a mess!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, you have no room to talk.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And look down.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No going back to sleep!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And {\i1}that's{\i0} why you're late?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It was by no means my fault!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If Sakura had gotten out of bed faster—
Dialogue: 15,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.39,Alternate,,0,0,0,,It's surprisingly stubborn.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop trying to force the knot out!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a morning nap?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 15,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:56.01,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An accident.
Dialogue: 15,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that those are magic words that can get you out of anything?!
Dialogue: 15,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And look.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I fell right back asleep.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you up all night?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 15,0:04:13.52,0:04:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I spent seven hours debating whether you would look better in green-framed or rimless glasses.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a way to spent seven hours...
Dialogue: 15,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparkle!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:25.82,0:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You took me completely by surprise!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The train is here.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Finals are just around the corner.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's obvious why we're reviewing this page in class, isn't it?
Dialogue: 15,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.38,Alternate,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakura! Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, going out of my way to help you,
Dialogue: 15,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but every now and then some people don't show any appreciation for...
Dialogue: 15,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...my goodwill!
Dialogue: 15,0:04:55.02,0:04:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be taking a week off for personal reasons starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 15,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, you'd better ask them today!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal reasons? Are you getting married?
Dialogue: 15,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Then revive and die a million times!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's brutal!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize that's verbal abuse, don't you?
Dialogue: 15,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll claim sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think I'll go easy on you just because you're a high schooler!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking it way too seriously.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm is coming.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's happening.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm...
Dialogue: 15,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! At long last, the Calm is coming!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's, like, something more important right now.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:30.72,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akkun, I heard that you, like, broke your promise with me and approached the Hollow Shadow.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, like, steaming mad!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, like, so upset that I couldn't even eat my sunflower seeds!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that she has a new character to play with every postcard she sends.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all kind of the same, though.
Dialogue: 15,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit calmly analyzing her!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And Kuriyama-san, why are you dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 15,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I-I was in the middle of work!
Dialogue: 15,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I never thought I'd ever have to wear something like this.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank goodness I had Sakura head home without me.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How unpleasant.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}So{\i0} unpleasant!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So Akkun, when did you, like, turn into such a little delinquent?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When I borrowed a dirty magazine from a friend, you went behind my back
Dialogue: 15,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and tore out the page that had a nude model wearing glasses.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It became your treasure!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:30.49,0:06:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has my pure-hearted, darling Akkun gone?
Dialogue: 15,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, like, devastated.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't making the right sound!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the small things like this that show her age.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, quit calmly analyzing her!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:45.52,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna run out of time if I keep this up!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to get to the heart of this letter.
Dialogue: 15,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm is coming!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm is, like, coming!
Dialogue: 15,0:06:57.39,0:07:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm is, like, totally coming!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:03.06,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you draw the line between "genius" and "insane"?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Not another word!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to be, like, extra careful!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:10.61,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise Yacchan you'll, like, be careful, Akkun!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you had to say?!
Dialogue: 15,0:07:17.29,0:07:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, the Calm refers to a period during which our demon powers are weakened.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your powers are weakened?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:23.42,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! I don't know the details, but according to the records,
Dialogue: 15,0:07:28.55,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,our innate vitality apparently drops dramatically.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, Exterminators are able to defeat demons
Dialogue: 15,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that are normally out of their league, so they're thrilled.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that case, why do I need to be careful?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanbara-kun, you are a half-demon.
Dialogue: 15,0:07:45.98,0:07:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If your demon powers weaken, what do you think would happen to you?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}would{\i0} happen?
Dialogue: 15,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Half-demons are too rare for me to know for certain,
Dialogue: 15,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but your immortality is one trait that you could temporarily lose.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And if an Exterminator found him in that vulnerable state,
Dialogue: 15,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a chance Akkey would be attacked.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Isn't that why you escorted him here?
Dialogue: 15,0:08:13.09,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, she said that the Calm does not start until midnight.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's just me, but I think the air feels somewhat heavy.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it's heavy. It feels very still.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What an appropriate name.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:32.74,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, I think my little sister and I...
Dialogue: 15,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,should walk home side by side.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's already gone.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she doesn't want to walk home with you.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she hates you.
Dialogue: 15,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're always acting like that!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:50.46,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, I'm going to miss the sale on frozen dinners if I don't hurry, so I've gotta run!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Later!
Dialogue: 15,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akkey!
Dialogue: 15,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take this lightly.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it in my chest.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a lift?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drop you off.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Calm, huh?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured we could have a \Ntalk while going out for a drive.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you about what you saw.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a demon?
Dialogue: 15,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Just like the Hollow Shadow,
Dialogue: 15,0:09:53.73,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,many of the more powerful demons lack a physical body.
Dialogue: 15,0:09:58.86,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that it takes years for these demons to come into physical being.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:03.79,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, they are born from the resentment and twisted hearts of countless people
Dialogue: 15,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,fusing together before eventually taking form.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:12.04,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If left alone, they could lead the world to ruin.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:16.30,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that these demons are the origin of disease, natural disasters, and war.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:21.89,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They are collectively referred to as "Beyond the Boundary".
Dialogue: 15,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the...
Dialogue: 15,0:10:28.01,0:10:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we're fortunate that only a fragment of this one has shown up.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't started to spread its influence yet.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:34.11,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me all of this?
Dialogue: 15,0:10:36.94,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Exterminator's Society has been keeping their eye on it for ages.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was made to believe that the tight-lipped Nase family has more information on it.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:45.37,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I would be able to get you to talk,
Dialogue: 15,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like the baby of the \Nfamily has been kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiimo.
Dialogue: 15,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 15,0:10:59.13,0:10:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:00.13,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the plan for subduing the demon you refer to as "Beyond the Boundary"?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:04.14,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Nase family going to annihilate it in secret?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get any info on that, either!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister is way too scary!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:12.15,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"But"?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna know?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakiimo!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 15,0:11:18.44,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I found some intriguing information regarding Kuriyama Mirai.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,About Kuriyama-san?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was digging around,
Dialogue: 15,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I found that the Inami family tried to kill Kuriyama Mirai
Dialogue: 15,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for murdering their daughter, Yui.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the one who stopped them...
Dialogue: 15,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was Nase Izumi.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:42.47,0:11:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that is somehow linked to this "Beyond the Boundary"?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 15,0:11:48.18,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't you find it fascinating if it was?
Dialogue: 15,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hassle.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you followed your little sister all of the way out here...
Dialogue: 15,0:12:12.72,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure looks like you've got a sister complex.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't just {\i1}look{\i0} like I do!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 15,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go ask your little sister!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that delicious little outburst.
Dialogue: 15,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 15,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Akihito-kun, you were hit by a car, so why...
Dialogue: 15,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did your injuries go?!
Dialogue: 15,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this—
Dialogue: 15,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 15,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 15,0:13:08.90,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What makes you think I would do that?
Dialogue: 15,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 15,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:39.79,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 15,0:13:43.46,0:13:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest for just a little longer.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for riding with us.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hananodera. This is Hananodera.
Dialogue: 15,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to take all of your belongings.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural to assume that the \NCalm had something to do with this.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:07.45,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I get the feeling that his human half has been greatly weakened along with his demon half.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything we can do to help him get better?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways to help humans
Dialogue: 15,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and ways to help demons to some extent,
Dialogue: 15,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but Kanbara-kun is a half-demon.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:23.62,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To be perfectly honest, half-demons are so rare, \NI don't really know what would help them recover.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 15,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, he's suffering from a \Nfever, so I brought some cool water.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of that!
Dialogue: 15,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should head home for now.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 15,0:14:43.65,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For the duration of the Calm, we can't go out in the open anyway.
Dialogue: 15,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting and watching Kanbara-kun sleep won't help him get better, now will it?
Dialogue: 15,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 15,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have school tomorrow as well?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When did Kanbara-senpai and Mirai meet?
Dialogue: 15,0:15:03.75,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. I don't know the details,
Dialogue: 15,0:15:07.09,0:15:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think they met shortly after Mirai-chan moved here.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, make sure to stay on your guard.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I planted the seeds.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that they should be ripe by now.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:26.59,0:15:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I've been chasing \Nafter since everything started.
Dialogue: 15,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I won't let the Nase family claim it.
