Dialogue: 2,0:15:38.04,0:15:38.87,Sign #3,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fax0.05\fay0.06\fs50\c&H91B8F5&\frz358.25\pos(795,477)}Full
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.04,0:15:38.87,Sign #3,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fax0.05\fay0.06\fs50\c&H91B8F5&\frz358.25\pos(795,477)}Full
Dialogue: 15,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 15,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...showtime!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected that to make so many pop out!
Dialogue: 15,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You stole my prey!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my eye on that one!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have it.
Dialogue: 15,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} here, too?!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Nase Izumi!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beast!
Dialogue: 15,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to stay out of her way.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:00.20,0:17:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In this area, the Nase family's authority is absolute.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In an attempt to create internal rifts,
Dialogue: 15,0:17:06.46,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,enemy powers have tried to stir up trouble more than once.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:10.78,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're saying everything \NFujima Miroku told me is a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.76,Sign #1,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs36\fax-0.5\frz358.5\c&H15111C&\pos(666,357)}Shindou Photo Studio
Dialogue: 15,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I said.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I cannot deny that is a distinct possibility.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:20.10,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi once warned me to be wary of the Exterminator's Society.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:25.35,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that the organization isn't on good terms with the Nase family.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't say anything when Kuriyama-san was gossiping about the Society a while back!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just tell everyone about that!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:36.50,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I haven't been told the full story myself.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to see Izumi-neesan!
Dialogue: 15,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to play dumb, and that will be the end of it.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something! She's your older sister, isn't she?
Dialogue: 15,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say the exact same thing to you.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Kuriyama-san.
Dialogue: 15,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Big Bro?
Dialogue: 15,0:18:01.35,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Akkey is...
Dialogue: 15,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon?!
Dialogue: 15,0:18:11.86,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One item for 280 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.03,Sign #5,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fry2\c&HDE5BF6&\fay0.04\an4\frz24\pos(434,381)}Message Sent
Dialogue: 15,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,one for 350 yen, and another for 10 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.12,Sign #8,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\blur2\fs70\an6\3c&H9869CD&\c&H9869CD&\pos(719,504)\alpha&H00&}Thank You Very Much
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.12,Sign #8,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs70\an6\c&H78979B&\pos(719,504)\alpha&H00&}Thank You Very Much
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.12,Sign #2,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs70\c&HAFADAB&\pos(742,230)}Yen
Dialogue: 15,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your total comes out to 1,870 yen.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?!
Dialogue: 15,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lost in thought and wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. More importantly, about Kanbara-senpai...
Dialogue: 15,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask again,
Dialogue: 15,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll let you stay with him.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:37.88,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like I could really do anything for him.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you want to stay by his side.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being unpleasant!
Dialogue: 15,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean it when you call someone unpleasant like that.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my sister told me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being unpleasant!
Dialogue: 15,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This time you truly meant it.
Dialogue: 15,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 15,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would stop you.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you want to be with Kanbara-senpai.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:05.12,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't really want to be with him or anything like that.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, I...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanbara-senpai loves glasses.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do with that!
Dialogue: 15,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normal around me.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm from a cursed clan...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I possess such abnormal powers...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He treats me like a normal person.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:28.66,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And always he has...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It must make you happy...
Dialogue: 15,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that you two met.
Dialogue: 15,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being unpleasant!
Dialogue: 15,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't mean it that time, either.
