Dialogue: 15,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya-chan...
Dialogue: 15,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai, go inside.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How may I help a member of the Exterminator's Society?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd find me.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should've expected it from a demon that can stand amongst Exterminators.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't intend to subdue me, do you?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 15,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply came to check on the situation here.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that it's come to this,
Dialogue: 15,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 15,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I am taking custody of Kanbara Akihito.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hand him over without any trouble.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear your reason why first.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I promised to look after Kanbara-kun.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to explain myself.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:36.54,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I doubt you'd believe me even if I did.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you truly believe I'd hand him over after hearing that?
Dialogue: 15,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's much stronger than I had anticipated.
Dialogue: 15,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm glad we're in the middle of the Calm.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even during the Calm, you're this powerful?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 15,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But how about this?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:38.56,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 15,0:21:40.98,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer girls who keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 15,0:21:46.95,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aya-chan...
Dialogue: 15,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
