Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:11.39,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Breaking through the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.35,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}hitsuzen toshite no kaikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.35,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We met in an inevitable encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.52,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}bokura no tame ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:17.52,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}For both our sakes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:20.02,ED-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}koukai wo nageku me ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:20.02,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}In your mournful eyes
