Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:11.87,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}That's how I always am
Dialogue: 15,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wish I never met him.
