Dialogue: 15,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm in front of Senpai.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:32.14,0:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kill him.
Dialogue: 15,0:23:33.30,0:23:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think that maybe, just maybe, I really am cursed.
